text: Wake Up with Al was a program on The Weather Channel that was hosted by Al Roker and Stephanie Abrams. It debuted on July 20, 2009, and ended on October 2, 2015, now replaced by AMHQ. Stephanie Abrams moved to AMHQ and replaced Sam Champion, while Al Roker remains at The Weather Channel.
